                <h5>全自動(dòng)反沖洗過濾器過濾的不是水是雜質(zhì)</h5>
                <h6>作者：北京羅道羅環(huán)保科技有限公司 時(shí)間：2021-07-13 瀏覽：<script src="/plus/count.php?view=yes&aid=901&mid=1" type='text/javascript' language="javascript"></script></h6>
                <div>
	　　隨著科技不斷的發(fā)展，各種設(shè)備技術(shù)不斷的更新進(jìn)步，全自動(dòng)反沖洗過濾器也不另外，公司生產(chǎn)的全自動(dòng)反沖洗過濾器在經(jīng)過多年的專研，技術(shù)不斷的創(chuàng)新，應(yīng)用到很多的領(lǐng)域。</div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>
<div>
	　　全自動(dòng)反沖洗過濾器產(chǎn)品特點(diǎn)明顯：高效，節(jié)能，安裝方便等。</div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>
<div>
	　　生產(chǎn)的<a >全自動(dòng)反沖洗過濾器</a>電器設(shè)備也進(jìn)行創(chuàng)新，采用了高效的人機(jī)界面，機(jī)械設(shè)備內(nèi)部采用智能高科技設(shè)計(jì)，通過外部連接的人機(jī)界面，能夠控制設(shè)備參數(shù)，從而控制設(shè)備過濾時(shí)間，排污時(shí)間等。不僅僅如此，我公司生產(chǎn)的設(shè)備都根據(jù)標(biāo)準(zhǔn)設(shè)計(jì)，不存在偷工減料問題。</div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>
<div>
	　　一直本著為社會(huì)做出貢獻(xiàn)的公司宗旨生產(chǎn)擁有自主知識(shí)產(chǎn)權(quán)的全自動(dòng)反沖洗過濾器、全自動(dòng)自清洗過濾器、壓差過濾器等產(chǎn)品，歡迎咨詢!</div>

class="sps-parkingpage__faq-wrapper"><h2 class="sps-parkingpage__heading sps-parkingpage__faq-title">Frequently asked questions</h2><h3 class="sps-parkingpage__faq-question">What is Spaceship?</h3><p class="sps-parkingpage__faq-answer">It's a digital platform that makes launching your online vision simple. Here, you can get all the tools you need to build your online presence, from domain names and shared hosting to encrypted email. Every website you create with us is automatically secured with domain privacy and a free SSL for 1 year.</p><h3 class="sps-parkingpage__faq-question">How do I choose the right domain name?</h3><p class="sps-parkingpage__faq-answer">A good domain name is short and memorable and ideally under 8 characters. A domain name is your online identity, so it’s important that it accurately represents your brand. That means picking both the right domain and domain extension (TLD). The most popular, classic TLDs include .com, .org, and .net. TLDs like .co, and .xyz are common within domain, crypto, and tech communities, while .ai has been rising in popularity in recent times.</p><h3 class="sps-parkingpage__faq-question">How do I create a website?</h3><p class="sps-parkingpage__faq-answer">Every great website name starts with a domain name. Once you pick the right name, choose from one of our Shared Hosting plans to get it online. Then it’s time to start designing your website.</p><h3 class="sps-parkingpage__faq-question">Do I need developers to start a website?</h3><p class="sps-parkingpage__faq-answer">Not at all. These days anyone can create a sleek website without the help of professionals. There are multiple content management systems available online that simplify the process with thousands of templates and plugins. WordPress is one of the most popular options, which you can install easily on Spaceship Hosting Manager.</p><h3 class="sps-parkingpage__faq-question">How do I make my website available to visitors?</h3><p class="sps-parkingpage__faq-answer">Unlike other web hosts that require users to point their domain to hosting via DNS records, Spaceship takes care of all that for you. Your domain and hosting plan will connect automatically during unboxing, so you don’t need to think about a thing.</p><h3 class="sps-parkingpage__faq-question">What is Unboxing?</h3><p class="sps-parkingpage__faq-answer">Unboxing is a simple way for you to connect your Spaceship products. You simply choose what you want to connect, and we do the rest.</p><h3 class="sps-parkingpage__faq-question">What is encrypted email?</h3><p class="sps-parkingpage__faq-answer">Whether you use your email for personal or business needs, encryption will protect you from data theft. Encrypted email cannot be hacked or read by unknown parties.</p><a class="gb-link gb-link-inverted sps-parkingpage__faq-link" onclick="window.location.href='https://www.spaceship.com/';">Still have questions?         <h1>Tuincentra in <span class="txt_orange">Nieuwleusen</span></h1>
        <p class="txt_slogan">Alles wat u wilt weten over shoppen in Nieuwleusen</p>

        <div class="tab-content">
            <div class="tab-pane active" id="welkom" role="tabpanel">
        <p><strong>Op <strong>123 Shoppen in Nieuwleusen</strong> vindt u allerlei informatie over shoppen in Nieuwleusen. Van Openingstijden tot tips over leuke winkeltjes, die een bezoekje waard zijn.
        Woont u in Nieuwleusen en bent u op zoek naar Tuincentra? Op Shoppen In vindt u relevante informatie over winkelen in Nieuwleusen. De place-to-be in Nieuwleusen, of gewoon een sigarenboertje op de hoek.</strong></p>
        <p>Naast onze uitgebreide informatie over winkelen in het algemeen, vindt u hier ook interessante links met betrekking tot winkelen, shoppen, fashion en het sluiten van goede deals.</p>
        <p>Verder probeert 123Shoppen in u op de hoogte te houden van de laatste ontwikkelingen op gebied van winkelen, winkelcentra, nieuws en must-have's.
        Daarnaast kunt u van ons en onze bezoekers handige tips verwachten met betrekking tot offline en online shoppen. Neem <a href="http://www.consuwijzer.nl/Uitgelicht/Winkelen_op_het_web" target="_blank">deze tip</a> nu bijvoorbeeld.</p>
        <p>Al met al willen wij u veel plezier wensen met het shopppen. Wij hopen u te kunnen voorzien van voldoende informatie. Mocht u nog iets missen, dan <a href="/contact/" class="scroll">horen wij dat graag</a>.
        </p>
        
        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-green pull-right next-tab" href="javascript:void(0)">Bekijk winkelcentra &amp; winkelstraten &rarr;</a>

            <h4>Kaart &amp; omgeving Nieuwleusen</h4>
            <p>Tuincentra omgeving van Nieuwleusen</p>
        <iframe width="100%" height="336" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" 
				src="//maps.google.nl/maps?hl=nl&amp;safe=off&amp;q=Tuincentra+in+Nieuwleusen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Tuincentra+in+Nieuwleusen&amp;hnear=Nieuwleusen&amp;t=m&amp;output=embed"></iframe>
				<p>Hierboven vindt u een een kaart met daarop een weergave van enkele winkels in Nieuwleusen. 
				U kunt ook een <a href="//maps.google.nl/maps?hl=nl&amp;safe=off&amp;q=Tuincentra+in+Nieuwleusen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=Tuincentra+in+Nieuwleusen&amp;hnear=Nieuwleusen&amp;t=m" target="_blank">grote kaart</a> bekijken in Google Maps</p>
				
				<br /><br />
				<a class="btn btn-lg btn-green pull-right next-tab" href="#kaart">Lees ons Blog over Nieuwleusen &rarr;</a>
        
				</div><div class="tab-pane" id="blog" role="tabpanel">
            <h3 class="kop">Blogs over winkels in Nieuwleusen</h3>
            <h4>Vrouwenlogica en mannelijk zwartkijken</h4>
            <p><small>10-2024, Nieuwleusen, door Inge S. (<strong>Redactie 123Shoppen.in</strong>)</small></p>
            <p><strong>Daar sta je dan: Met je ziel onder je arm, midden in Nieuwleusen. Min of meer verdwaald. Hoe kan het ook anders, ik was nog nooit eerder in Nieuwleusen wezen winkelen.
            Gelukkig duurde het niet lang voor ik de Tuincentra ontdekt had. Waarschijnlijk viel het de medewerker van des betreffende zaak ook op, dat ik mij nog niet geheel een vis in het water voelde, hier in het vreemde.</strong></p>
            <p>Het was dan ook een hele opluchting ik ik met een tas vol nieuwe spulletjes weer buiten op de stoep stond. Ik had weer even goede deals gesloten. Een bekwaam onderhandelaar, zo zou ik mezelf willen omschrijven. Mijn man zegt altijd dat het typisch vrouwen logica is: 'Ik heb vandaag weer 40% bespaard!'. Hij heeft het altijd over die 60% die ik uitgeef. Echt typisch mannelijk zwartkijken. Het glas is altijd half leeg als je het hem vraagt.</p>
            
            <p>Nee, laat ons vrouwen maar lekker besparen hoor. Als iedereen zo zou besparen als ons, was er van een crisis waarschijnlijk geen sprake geweest. Daar herken je de mannenwereld dus aan he. Bezuinigen, bezuinigen en nog eens bezuinigen. Geld moet rollen. Dus na een kort bezoekje aan een aantal andere winkeltjes in Nieuwleusen, heb ik mezelf getrakteerd op patatje - slecht voor de lijn, maar O zo goed voor m'n humeur - dat had ik wel verdiend. </p>
            <p>Wederom een succesvolle dag winkelen, ditmaal in Nieuwleusen voltooid. Jammer, ik begon het hier net zo leuk te vinden.</p> 

            
            <p><small>Ook een blog insturen? <a href="mailto:info@123shoppen.in">Laat het ons weten!</a> Stuur een bericht naar info@123shoppen.in met als onderwerp 'Blog'.</small></p>
            <a class="btn btn-lg btn-green pull-right next-tab" href="#kaart">Volgende &rarr;</a>
        	</div><div class="tab-pane" id="vervoer" role="tabpanel">
		    <h4>Vervoer van en naar Nieuwleusen</h4>
            <p>Klaar om te vertrekken en lekker een dagje te gaan shoppen? Als je naar Nieuwleusen gaat, is het belangrijk op de hoogte te zijn van de mogelijkheden met betrekking tot vervoer in en naar Nieuwleusen.</p>
            <p>Twee dingen die belangrijk zijn wanneer u met de auto naar Nieuwleusen gaat. Ten eerste een plek waar u makkelijk (en voordelig) kunt parkeren, en ten tweede hoe u op die plek komt.
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://123shoppen.in/Nieuwleusen/Parkeren/">Vindt een parkeergelegenheid in Nieuwleusen</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.google.nl/maps/place/Nieuwleusen/" target="_blank">Plan uw route naar Nieuwleusen met behulp van Google Maps</a></li>
            </ul>
            <img src="https://123shoppen.in/uploads/images/shoppen-met-de-auto.jpg" class="img-responsive col-sm-4" /> 
            <h4>Met het openbaar vervoer</h4>
			<h5>9292OV</h5>
            <p>De missie van 9292 is om alle mensen die betrokken zijn bij het openbaar vervoer te ontzorgen. 
            Dit betekent dat we jou als reiziger de informatie willen geven die je nodig hebt om te reizen met het openbaar vervoer. 
            Daarnaast willen we ook de OV-bedrijven, overheden en het bedrijfsleven ondersteunen bij het uitvoeren van hun taken binnen het openbaar vervoer.</p>
            <p><a href="http://9292.nl/?naar=Nieuwleusen" target="_blank">Plan eenvoudig uw reis naar Nieuwleusen met 9292ov.nl</a></p>
				<!-- 9292 widget v1 -->
				<!-- 9292 widget v1 -->
            		
            <br /><br />

            </div><div class="tab-pane" id="parkeren" role="tabpanel">
        <h4>Parkeren in Nieuwleusen</h4>
        <p>Waar kun je je auto kwijt en wat zijn de parkeerkosten? Dingen die belangrijk zijn voor een geslaagd dagje shoppen. Gebruik daarom deze handige kaart waar je kunt inzoom en scrollen. Klik op een P om direct het parkeertarief van die zone te bekijken.
        Gebruik de handige filters om overdekte en of oplaadpunten voor elektrische auto's te vinden.
        </p>
        <iframe src="//www.prettigparkeren.nl/embed/#!Nieuwleusen/////" width="100%" height="500" frameborder="0"></iframe>

function MM_swapImgRestore() { //v3.0
  var i,x,a=document.MM_sr; for(i=0;a&&i<a.length&&(x=a[i])&&x.oSrc;i++) x.src=x.oSrc;
}

function MM_preloadImages() { //v3.0
  var d=document; if(d.images){ if(!d.MM_p) d.MM_p=new Array();

}

function MM_findObj(n, d) { //v4.01
  var p,i,x;  if(!d) d=document; if((p=n.indexOf("?"))>0&&parent.frames.length) {
    d=parent.frames[n.substring(p+1)].document; n=n.substring(0,p);}
  if(!(x=d[n])&&d.all) x=d.all[n]; for (i=0;!x&&i<d.forms.length;i++) x=d.forms[i][n];
  for(i=0;!x&&d.layers&&i<d.layers.length;i++) x=MM_findObj(n,d.layers[i].document);
  if(!x && d.getElementById) x=d.getElementById(n); return x;
}

}

      <script>
		Banner003113('.Banner003113')
		function Banner003113(v) {
			var _this = $(v)
			var _total = _this.find(".total")
			var _slider = _this.find(".slider")
			var _li = _this.find('.slider li').length
			var _btn = _this.find(".controls dd")
			var _dots = _this.find(".controls dt.dots")
			_total.text("0" + _li)
			_slider.slick({
				autoplay: true,
				dots: true,
				autoplaySpeed:5000,
				appendArrows: _btn,
				customPaging: function(slider, i) {
					return $('<span tabindex="0" />').text("0" + (i + 1));
				},
				appendDots: _dots
			});
			_this.find(".slick-current").addClass("ani-show")
			_slider.on('afterChange', function(event, slick, currentSlide, nextSlide) {
				_this.find(".slick-slide").eq(currentSlide + 1).addClass("ani-show").siblings().removeClass("ani-show")
			});
		}
	</script> 
    </section>
  </section>

$(".Map002793 .tab_span li").click(function(e) {
	var e = $(this).index();
	$(this).addClass("on");
	$(this).siblings().removeClass("on");
	$(".Map002793 .tab_list .box").hide();
	$(".Map002793 .tab_list .box").eq(e).show();
});
$(".Map002793 .tab_span li").eq(0).click();
</script>

	setTimeout(function() {
		console.log('ddddddd');
		$(".slider-tpye li").eq(0).addClass("on");
		$(".slider-tpyeCon .tpyeCon-item").eq(1).addClass("hide");
		$(".slider-tpyeCon .tpyeCon-item").eq(2).addClass("hide");
		$(".slider-tpyeCon .tpyeCon-item").eq(3).addClass("hide");
	}, 1000)

	$(".slider-tpye li").click(function() {
		$(this).addClass("on").siblings().removeClass("on");
		var i = $(this).index();
		$(".slider-tpyeCon .tpyeCon-item").eq(i).siblings().addClass("hide");
		$(".slider-tpyeCon .tpyeCon-item").eq(i).removeClass("hide");

	})
</script>

 <li class="last">無くなる前にどうぞ。半袖シャツ　STILL　BY　HAND（ｽﾃｨﾙﾊﾞｲﾊﾝﾄﾞ）ー大阪SECONDー</li>

<div id="main_col">

 
 <div id="article">
  <p id="post_date_headline"><time class="entry-date updated" datetime="2019-06-16T07:19:53+00:00">2019.06.16</time></p>  <h2 id="post_title">無くなる前にどうぞ。半袖シャツ　STILL　BY　HAND（ｽﾃｨﾙﾊﾞｲﾊﾝﾄﾞ）ー大阪SECONDー</h2>
    <div id="post_image">
      <div id="gallery">
    <img width="760" height="460" src="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-760x460.jpg" class="attachment-size5 size-size5 wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-760x460.jpg 760w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-330x200.jpg 330w" sizes="(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px" />   </div>
      <div id="image_meta" class="clearfix">
        <ul class="clearfix">
          <li class="category"><a href="http://2-second.com/category/brand/mens/still-by-hand/" rel="category tag">STILL BY HAND</a>, <a href="http://2-second.com/category/%ef%bc%92%ef%bc%90%ef%bc%91%ef%bc%99%e3%80%80%ef%bd%93%ef%bd%93%e3%80%80%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%9c/" rel="category tag">２０１９　ＳＳ　新作</a></li>    </ul>
   </div>
  </div><!-- END #post_image -->
  
  <div class="post_content clearfix">
   <p>こんにちは！SECONDの山本です。<br />
今日は父の日ですね。心なしか、家族連れのお客様が多いです(^^)</p>
<p>皆様、プレゼントはお決まりですか？？</p>
<p>今日は、残りわずか！STILL BY HAND(スティルバイハンド) 半袖シャツのご紹介です！<br />
<img loading="lazy" src="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o7-1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9822" srcset="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o7-1.jpg 800w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o7-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o7-1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o7-1-768x768.jpg 768w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o7-1-200x200.jpg 200w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o7-1-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><br />
昨年も人気だった無双仕立ての半袖シャツ。<br />
今年は暑くなるのが早かったので、ブランド側にも在庫が無く、SECONDでも店頭にあるだけです。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9823" srcset="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1.jpg 800w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-768x768.jpg 768w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-200x200.jpg 200w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142344163_o6-1-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><br />
ガーゼの様な光沢のある薄いコットン生地を2枚仕立てにしてあります。一枚で着られて涼しく、軽いです♪<br />
きれいめ感があるので、クールビズ用にされる方も。</p>
<p>ありそうでない、青みがかったブラックともいえるナイトブルーネイビーが、カジュアルにもきれいめにも対応してくれます！</p>
<p>お次はこちら。<br />
<img loading="lazy" src="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o2-1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9825" srcset="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o2-1.jpg 800w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o2-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o2-1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o2-1-768x768.jpg 768w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o2-1-200x200.jpg 200w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o2-1-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><br />
キュプラが入ったシャリ感のあるシャツです。ポケット付きで、先ほどのシャツよりもカジュアルですね。<br />
<img loading="lazy" src="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654-1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9824" srcset="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654-1.jpg 800w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654-1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654-1-768x768.jpg 768w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654-1-200x200.jpg 200w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654-1-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><br />
ほどよいBOXシルエットで肌に纏わりつきません♪<br />
生地がこんなに薄いんです。<br />
<img loading="lazy" src="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o6-1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9826" srcset="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o6-1.jpg 800w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o6-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o6-1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o6-1-768x768.jpg 768w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o6-1-200x200.jpg 200w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o6-1-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><br />
しかもキュプラは、吸湿、放湿に富む性質があります。<br />
着ているだけで、湿度を快適に保ってくれます！</p>
<p>色違いのベージュ。<br />
<img loading="lazy" src="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o8-1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9827" srcset="http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o8-1.jpg 800w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o8-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o8-1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o8-1-768x768.jpg 768w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o8-1-200x200.jpg 200w, http://2-second.com/new/wp-content/uploads/142850654_o8-1-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><br />
羽織物にもぴったりです♪</p>
<p>カジュアルすぎない質感、シルエット、着心地。<br />
父の日のプレゼントに、ご自分用にも。<br />
STILL　BY HANDのシャツ、一枚いかがでしょうか？？<br />
店頭に並んであるだけになりました。どうぞお早めに！</p>
<p class="webbtn"><a href="http://second2.shop-pro.jp/?pid=142344163" target="_blank" rel="noopener">still by hand 無双ローン半袖シャツはこちらから</a></p>
<p class="webbtn"><a href="http://second2.shop-pro.jp/?pid=142850654" target="_blank" rel="noopener">still by hand キュプラ混半袖シャツはこちらから</a></p>
<p>＊直接お電話での「通販」も可能です。　お気軽にお問い合わせください</p>
<p>是非　気になる方は試着しに来てくださいね<br />
直接お電話での通販も可能です。<br />
お気軽にお問い合わせください。<br />
大阪市北区梅田1丁目12-6　ｲｰﾏ3F<br />
06-6341-1285<br />
OPEN　11:00～21:00</p>

function CHAT_GO123(AID){

  document.form1_GO.ROOM.value=AID;

  if(document.form1_GO.uname.value=="")    {
    alert("пJʺ");

}

function MM_swapImgRestore() { //v3.0
  var i,x,a=document.MM_sr; for(i=0;a&&i<a.length&&(x=a[i])&&x.oSrc;i++) x.src=x.oSrc;
}

function MM_preloadImages() { //v3.0
  var d=document; if(d.images){ if(!d.MM_p) d.MM_p=new Array();
    var i,j=d.MM_p.length,a=MM_preloadImages.arguments; for(i=0; i<a.length; i++)
    if (a[i].indexOf("#")!=0){ d.MM_p[j]=new Image; d.MM_p[j++].src=a[i];}}
}

function MM_findObj(n, d) { //v4.01
  var p,i,x;  if(!d) d=document; if((p=n.indexOf("?"))>0&&parent.frames.length) {
    d=parent.frames[n.substring(p+1)].document; n=n.substring(0,p);}
  if(!(x=d[n])&&d.all) x=d.all[n]; for (i=0;!x&&i<d.forms.length;i++) x=d.forms[i][n];
  for(i=0;!x&&d.layers&&i<d.layers.length;i++) x=MM_findObj(n,d.layers[i].document);
  if(!x && d.getElementById) x=d.getElementById(n); return x;
}

function MM_swapImage() { //v3.0
  var i,j=0,x,a=MM_swapImage.arguments; document.MM_sr=new Array; for(i=0;i<(a.length-2);i+=3)
   if ((x=MM_findObj(a[i]))!=null){document.MM_sr[j++]=x; if(!x.oSrc) x.oSrc=x.src; x.src=a[i+2];}
}

				<script>
					function show( watch_url ) {
						window.open( watch_url, 'watchlive', 'height=915,width=640', false );
					}
					function exec_watch_live( watch_url ) {
						if ( typeof ssoObj !== 'undefined' ) {
							ssoObj.env_var.state.watch = true;
							ssoObj.function.initialiseCallback( function(cb) {
								if ( typeof cb === 'string' && cb === 'unauthenticated' || typeof cb === "undefined" || cb === null ) {
									// User is not logged in
									ssoObj.function.redirectLogin();
								} else if ( typeof cb === 'object' ) {
									// User is logged in
									// Launch the video
									show(watch_url);
									sessionStorage.removeItem('watch');
									ssoObj.env_var.state.watch = false;
									// Reload the page to refresh Username
									location.reload();
								}
							})
						} else {
							show( watch_url );
						}
						
					}
				</script>

				<div class="watch_sec" onclick="exec_watch_live( 'index-3.html' );">

<script>

jQuery(function () {
	if ( typeof mml_compliance !== 'undefined' ) {
		// When SSO is disabled 
		mml_compliance.get_are_cookies_allowed_async( function ( cookies_allowed ) {
			if ( ! cookies_allowed ) {
				jQuery( '.mml-gdpr-notification-footer' ).show();
			}
		} );
	}
});

function mml_cookie_notification_dismiss() {
	jQuery( '.mml-gdpr-notification-footer' ).fadeOut();
}

function mml_cookie_notification_accept() {
	mml_compliance.set_are_cookies_allowed( true );
	jQuery( '.mml-gdpr-notification-footer' ).fadeOut();
}

</script>

            return function () {
                sA.p = cb();
                sA.queue.push({f: e, a: arguments});

        }

                return 0;
            })
        };

            return function () {

        <h1>敬天爱人   以禾为本</h1>

        <div class="aboutdiv">
          <h2 class="proshowh3 text-center">&#28595;&#38376;&#32654;&#39640;&#26757;&#36172;&#22330;简介</h2>          <div class="fnt_16">            <p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&#28595;&#38376;&#32654;&#39640;&#26757;&#21338;&#24425;&#23448;&#26041;&#32593;&#31449;成立于</span><span style="font-family:宋体">1995年，是集科研、生产、</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">销售于一体的国家高新技术企业</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。公司地处温州瓯江南畔（瓯江大桥南首</span><span style="font-family:宋体">100米），现已形成了以浙江为总部经济的发展模式，拥有浙江、江苏、四川3个生产基地，总占地900余亩，员工1300余人。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #262626; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">二十多年来，&#28595;&#38376;&#32654;&#39640;&#26757;&#36172;&#22330;专注于化工领域的研究与生产，连续多年被评为农药行业销售30强，公司现有原药产品60多个，产品具有低毒、新颖、技术优越、附加值高等特点，技术起点高、市场销售稳定，产品70%出口，销售网络遍布全国各地、全球80多个国家和地区，有相对稳定的客户，与跨国公司、世界五百强</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #262626; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">企业</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #262626; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;">也开展了合作，是甲霜灵、有机锡、丙环唑、辛酰溴苯腈、苯醚甲环唑、精甲霜灵、噻螨酮、霜霉威盐酸盐、异噁草松等产品的全球主要生产供应商。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">   公司创立至今，坚持</span><span style="font-family:宋体">“科技创业、质量立业”的方针，全力打造一个有竞争力的现代化企业，并推进企业可持续的发展战略，通过了ISO9001质量管理体系认证、ISO14001环境管理体系认证、ISO18000职业健康安全管理体系认证，获得“浙江省亩均效益领跑企业”“浙江省著名商标”“浙江省出口名牌”“浙江省清洁生产阶段性成果企业”“温州市创新型领军（瞪羚）</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">企业</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">”“温州百强企业”“温州市制造业企业五十强”“温州市出口龙头企业”“温州市专利示范企业”“温州市安全文化建设示范企业”<span style="color: #262626; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;">“温州市实力名企百强”</span>等荣誉称号。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&#28595;&#38376;&#32654;&#39640;&#26757;&#36172;&#22330;的辉煌，源自二十</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">多年</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #262626;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的艰辛创业</span><span style="font-family:宋体">!如今的&#28595;&#38376;&#32654;&#39640;&#26757;&#36172;&#22330;人正以更稳健的脚步，更严格的要求，更自信的姿态，迈开了打造规模化、现代化企业的豪迈步伐，努力把&#28595;&#38376;&#32654;&#39640;&#26757;&#36172;&#22330;建设成为一个有竞争力的现代化上市企业，打造真正的绿色化工，实现与自然、与社会的和谐共荣!</span></span></p><p><br/></p>          </div>
          <div class="row">                        <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 aboutlink">              <a href="http://2j.danielkang.net/Col/Col7/Index.aspx">                <img alt="" src="/Template/Default/Column/20190618110927907.jpg"/>                <span class="fnt_16">研发实力</span>              </a>            </div>                        <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 aboutlink">              <a href="http://2j.danielkang.net/Col/Col8/Index.aspx">                <img alt="" src="/Template/Default/Column/20190618110928014.jpg"/>                <span class="fnt_16">质量管理</span>              </a>            </div>                        <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 aboutlink">              <a href="http://2j.danielkang.net/Col/Col9/Index.aspx">                <img alt="" src="/Template/Default/Column/20190618110928107.jpg"/>                <span class="fnt_16">荣誉资质</span>              </a>            </div>                        <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 aboutlink">              <a href="http://2j.danielkang.net/Col/Col10/Index.aspx">                <img alt="" src="/Template/Default/Column/20190618110927960.jpg"/>                <span class="fnt_16">三大基地</span>              </a>            </div>                      </div>

<<h1>OSCARO.COM : Un partenaire de choix pour vos pièces auto</h1> </div>
<div class="col col-sm-8">
<p>Fond&eacute; en 2001, Oscaro.com s&rsquo;est impos&eacute; en quelques ann&eacute;es pour devenir un acteur incontournable dans la fourniture de pi&egrave;ces et d&rsquo;accessoires automobiles, avec pas moins de 20.000 commandes trait&eacute;es par mois. Pl&eacute;biscit&eacute; par les consommateurs qui l&rsquo;ont hiss&eacute; dans le top 5 des meilleurs sites e-marchands pour l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e 2016, Oscaro.com est le leader en mati&egrave;re d&rsquo;achat de pi&egrave;ces auto.</p><h2>L&rsquo;assurance d&rsquo;un choix de qualit&eacute; au meilleur co&ucirc;t</h2><p>Se fournissant chez les plus grands &eacute;quipementiers automobiles et leurs partenaires, Oscaro.com vous propose un large choix de pi&egrave;ces neuves, garanties d&rsquo;origine. Cette absence d&rsquo;interm&eacute;diaire permet de proposer un juste prix avec une &eacute;conomie de 30 &agrave; 60 % par rapport aux fili&egrave;res classiques. <br/> L&rsquo;achat se fait en toute tranquillit&eacute; avec l&rsquo;assurance de b&eacute;n&eacute;ficier de la garantie de conformit&eacute; et de la garantie des vices cach&eacute;s. <a href="http://www.societe.com/societe/oscaro-com-434474284.html">De plus, Oscaro.com</a> reprend et rembourse tout article qui ne vous satisferait pas sous un d&eacute;lai de 365 jours. Un accompagnement id&eacute;al</p><ul><li>180 experts en m&eacute;canique disponibles pour vous aider sur le choix des pi&egrave;ces</li><li>Un forum communautaire d&rsquo;entraide</li><li>Des tutoriels valid&eacute;s par nos experts</li><li>Des vid&eacute;os th&eacute;matiques sur youtube</li></ul><p>vous aideront et vous guideront pas &agrave; pas.</p><h3>Des services suppl&eacute;mentaires</h3><p>Oscaro.com propose &agrave; ses clients de leur faciliter la vie en leur proposant un panel de services sur mesure, des <a href="http://www.concours-oscaro.com/">jeux concours</a>, de nombreuses id&eacute;es cadeaux (surtout pour les hommes!) et bien plus encore.</p><h4>Un paiement s&eacute;curis&eacute; et facilit&eacute;</h4><p>Le paiement peut s&rsquo;effectuer en toute s&eacute;curit&eacute; par tout moyen (Carte bancaire, paypal, paylib&hellip;) et vous avez la possibilit&eacute; de payer en plusieurs fois pour les achats sup&eacute;rieurs &agrave; 150 &euro;.</p><h3>Une livraison simple et rapide</h3><p>24 &agrave; 48 h apr&egrave;s la pr&eacute;paration de la commande, la livraison est effectu&eacute;e &agrave; domicile ou dans un point relais de votre choix.</p> </div>
<div class="col col-sm-4">
<img src="https://consomatique.fr/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/oscaro.png" class="img-responsive" alt>
</div>

function CHAT_GO(AID,FORMNAME){

document.form1_GO.ROOM.value=AID;
document.form1_GO.MID.value=10000;
if(FORMNAME.uname.value=="" || FORMNAME.uname.value.indexOf("пJ")!=-1)    {
  alert("пJʺ");
  FORMNAME.uname.focus();
}else{
  var AWidth = screen.width-20;
  var AHeight = screen.height-80;
  if( document.all || document.layers ){
  utchat10000=window.open("","utchat10000","width="+AWidth+",height="+AHeight+",resizable=yes,toolbar=no,location=no,directories=no,status=no,menubar=no,copyhistory=no,top=0,left=0");
  }else{
  utchat10000=window.open("","utchat10000","width="+AWidth+",height="+AHeight+",resizable=yes,toolbar=no,location=no,directories=no,status=no,menubar=no,copyhistory=no,top=0,left=0");
  }
  document.form1_GO.uname.value=FORMNAME.uname.value;
  document.form1_GO.sex.value=FORMNAME.sex.value;
  document.form1_GO.submit();
}
}

function MM_swapImgRestore() { //v3.0
  var i,x,a=document.MM_sr; for(i=0;a&&i<a.length&&(x=a[i])&&x.oSrc;i++) x.src=x.oSrc;
}

function MM_preloadImages() { //v3.0
  var d=document; if(d.images){ if(!d.MM_p) d.MM_p=new Array();
    var i,j=d.MM_p.length,a=MM_preloadImages.arguments; for(i=0; i<a.length; i++)
    if (a[i].indexOf("#")!=0){ d.MM_p[j]=new Image; d.MM_p[j++].src=a[i];}}
}

function MM_findObj(n, d) { //v4.01
  var p,i,x;  if(!d) d=document; if((p=n.indexOf("?"))>0&&parent.frames.length) {
    d=parent.frames[n.substring(p+1)].document; n=n.substring(0,p);}
  if(!(x=d[n])&&d.all) x=d.all[n]; for (i=0;!x&&i<d.forms.length;i++) x=d.forms[i][n];
  for(i=0;!x&&d.layers&&i<d.layers.length;i++) x=MM_findObj(n,d.layers[i].document);
  if(!x && d.getElementById) x=d.getElementById(n); return x;
}

function MM_swapImage() { //v3.0
  var i,j=0,x,a=MM_swapImage.arguments; document.MM_sr=new Array; for(i=0;i<(a.length-2);i+=3)
   if ((x=MM_findObj(a[i]))!=null){document.MM_sr[j++]=x; if(!x.oSrc) x.oSrc=x.src; x.src=a[i+2];}
}

高雄市第一藥師公會年終聯歡會 感恩與傳承
◎文／高雄記者吳宜庭
高雄市第一藥師公會112年度的會員年終聯歡會特別的不同，除感謝一同經歷艱辛與努力為疫情付出的藥師們，更是傳承交接的美好夜晚。
112年12月17日當天，急驟10度的寒流也凍不住藥師的熱情和歡喜，大家齊聚為這場感恩餐會及交接典禮共同揭開序幕。
高雄市衛生局長黃志中頒發「COVID-19防疫核心藥局貢獻獎」，感謝旗山區的林錦良藥師、岡山區的朱千晟藥師及鳳山區的吳文嘉藥師，從口罩實名制到送藥到府服務，於疫情期間第一線維護社區民眾健康，功不可沒。高雄市毒品防制局長林瑩蓉頒發第23屆協辦社區、校園用藥及毒品宣導有功人員，分別是主委曾金課及三區組長：陳聰輝、鄭明達、林錦良。
會中舉辦理事長交接典禮，由前理事長劉亮君交接印信到新任理事長戴慶玲手中，過程感人且激勵人心。感恩前理事長為藥師的權益努力，新任理事長接棒與新任理監事將共同努力，讓藥師有更美好的未來。

↑高雄市第一藥師公會於112年12月17日舉辦112年度的會員年終聯歡會。

    d=parent.frames[n.substring(p+1)].document; n=n.substring(0,p);}

}

  var i,x,a=document.MM_sr; for(i=0;a&&i<a.length&&(x=a[i])&&x.oSrc;i++) x.src=x.oSrc;
}

function MM_preloadImages() { //v3.0
  var d=document; if(d.images){ if(!d.MM_p) d.MM_p=new Array();
    var i,j=d.MM_p.length,a=MM_preloadImages.arguments; for(i=0; i<a.length; i++)
    if (a[i].indexOf("#")!=0){ d.MM_p[j]=new Image; d.MM_p[j++].src=a[i];}}
}

function MM_findObj(n, d) { //v4.01
  var p,i,x;  if(!d) d=document; if((p=n.indexOf("?"))>0&&parent.frames.length) {
    d=parent.frames[n.substring(p+1)].document; n=n.substring(0,p);}
  if(!(x=d[n])&&d.all) x=d.all[n]; for (i=0;!x&&i<d.forms.length;i++) x=d.forms[i][n];
  for(i=0;!x&&d.layers&&i<d.layers.length;i++) x=MM_findObj(n,d.layers[i].document);
  if(!x && d.getElementById) x=d.getElementById(n); return x;
}

function MM_swapImage() { //v3.0
  var i,j=0,x,a=MM_swapImage.arguments; document.MM_sr=new Array; for(i=0;i<(a.length-2);i+=3)
   if ((x=MM_findObj(a[i]))!=null){document.MM_sr[j++]=x; if(!x.oSrc) x.oSrc=x.src; x.src=a[i+2];}
}

<meta content='5395099626833262967' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='5395099626833262967'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
Ice, Snow and Frigid Air--Tomorrow 70 Degrees!
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-5395099626833262967' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<span style="font-size: large;">Hi guys! I'm just staying in today because we have ice, sleet, rain and snow today. It is SO cold and windy. As is typical for Oklahoma, tomorrow it will be sunny and 70 degrees. My sinus cavities are going crazy. Lola is mad a me because we aren't driving anywhere today. She sat and stared at me until I got up and followed her and she went right to the door to the garage and sat there. She thinks I'm slow and just don't get it. I'm finishing the rows for the Tulip Patch quilt--here they are just hanging . I only have one more tulip row and 2 more filler rows to go and then I can put it together.&nbsp;</span><br />
<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhSbw1d8L6DoauQsqWxTTeodWd3m-cNBCG2pxcQ9dTFBmSG-5PQHRtxE0YUFZmeRks1ygf6gUuQk8mXyZzEYNoAeAA98zQQci2EzKTP1XKp0ZNX7bgPNus20hh2RO-_emXOrysi4-WSuk0/s1600/002.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="640" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhSbw1d8L6DoauQsqWxTTeodWd3m-cNBCG2pxcQ9dTFBmSG-5PQHRtxE0YUFZmeRks1ygf6gUuQk8mXyZzEYNoAeAA98zQQci2EzKTP1XKp0ZNX7bgPNus20hh2RO-_emXOrysi4-WSuk0/s1600/002.JPG" width="361" /></a></div>
<br />
<span style="font-size: large;">It's so cheerful and bright that it makes me think of spring. I'm also doing more blocks for the FlowerBoxSewAlong from Lori Holt. The link to her blog and that pattern is <a href="http://beeinmybonnetco.blogspot.com/2015/02/my-flower-box-quilt-block-tutorial-and.html" target="_blank"><span style="color: red;">HERE</span>. </a>It's a fun, quick block to make.&nbsp;</span><br />
<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkcjLu83Aj1BKPVJWC9Oxrq34syJ0OCwS5mkYV4ydDdULEkvN1Bbu1YIyf7tOUZ80wRtD7y1j7vrfyU7bMZTaH_a-wq6a_P5DfZ1tEtWJiOZF-MyV4g7hzdLdkj68MPipCetmWfVhj0F8/s1600/Block+One.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="385" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkcjLu83Aj1BKPVJWC9Oxrq34syJ0OCwS5mkYV4ydDdULEkvN1Bbu1YIyf7tOUZ80wRtD7y1j7vrfyU7bMZTaH_a-wq6a_P5DfZ1tEtWJiOZF-MyV4g7hzdLdkj68MPipCetmWfVhj0F8/s1600/Block+One.jpg" width="400" /></a></div>
<br />
<span style="font-size: large;">That's about all I can handle right now although I have tons of things I can work on. What are you doing today? Do you have a Wednesday WIP? Well, take care! XO from Bev</span>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-footer'>

<script type="text/javascript">
    window.followersIframe = null;
    function followersIframeOpen(url) {
      gapi.load("gapi.iframes", function() {
        if (gapi.iframes && gapi.iframes.getContext) {
          window.followersIframe = gapi.iframes.getContext().openChild({
            url: url,
            where: document.getElementById("followers-iframe-container"),
            messageHandlersFilter: gapi.iframes.CROSS_ORIGIN_IFRAMES_FILTER,
            messageHandlers: {
              '_ready': function(obj) {
                window.followersIframe.getIframeEl().height = obj.height;
              },
              'reset': function() {
                window.followersIframe.close();
                followersIframeOpen("https://www.blogger.com/followers/frame/7842868385255955219?colors\x3dCgt0cmFuc3BhcmVudBILdHJhbnNwYXJlbnQaByM2NjY2NjYiByM5OWNjY2MqByNmZmZmZmYyByMwMDAwMDA6ByM2NjY2NjZCByM5OWNjY2NKByM5OTk5OTlSByM5OWNjY2NaC3RyYW5zcGFyZW50\x26pageSize\x3d21\x26hl\x3den\x26origin\x3dhttp://44thstreetfabric.blogspot.com");
              },
              'open': function(url) {
                window.followersIframe.close();
                followersIframeOpen(url);
              },
              'blogger-ping': function() {
              }
            }
          });
        }
      });
    }
    followersIframeOpen("https://www.blogger.com/followers/frame/7842868385255955219?colors\x3dCgt0cmFuc3BhcmVudBILdHJhbnNwYXJlbnQaByM2NjY2NjYiByM5OWNjY2MqByNmZmZmZmYyByMwMDAwMDA6ByM2NjY2NjZCByM5OWNjY2NKByM5OTk5OTlSByM5OWNjY2NaC3RyYW5zcGFyZW50\x26pageSize\x3d21\x26hl\x3den\x26origin\x3dhttp://44thstreetfabric.blogspot.com");

</div><div class='widget Text' data-version='1' id='Text2'>
<h2 class='title'>To All My Dogs Who Have Gone On Before Me</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
"The moment that you left me,<br/>my heart was split in two;<br/>one side was filled with<br/>memories; the other side<br/>died with you.<br/>I often lay awake at night when<br/>the world is fast asleep;<br/>and take a walk down memory<br/>lane with tears upon my cheek.<br/>Remembering you is easy,<br/>I do it every day;<br/>but missing you is a heartache<br/>that never goes away.<br/>I hold you tightly within my heart<br/>and there you will remain;<br/>you see, life has gone on<br/>without you, but will never be<br/>the same". Blair Robertson<br/>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
</div><div class='widget Text' data-version='1' id='Text3'>
<h2 class='title'>An Important Personal Message</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<b>My dear friends - Have you noticed that the world seems to be getting more and more evil and corrupt? Have you ever wondered, assuming that Revelations is true, where we are time-wise and what will happen in the last days? At the bottom of this page, there is a 7 minute video that has no narration, just Bible facts about the sequence of events and where we might be. Of course, some of you won't think this is important, some of you might look at the video to see what the Bible does say and some of you may be offended and unfollow me. I personally believe that time is short. We are at 30 seconds to midnight. Things are coming this year that will affect the USA. Watch or not. I mean no offense. If I believe there is something to warn you about and I don't do it, I will be held accountable. I care about what happens to all of us. In love!</b><br />
</div>

function check_input(FORMNAME){

    alert('жgTb!!');
    FORMNAME.USERID.focus();
    return false;
  }
  if (FORMNAME.USER_PASSWORD.value==''){
    alert('жgTKX!!');
    FORMNAME.USER_PASSWORD.focus();
    return false;
  }
  if (FORMNAME.CHIMG.value==''){
    alert('жgT[Ϥ]ϤW5XƦr!!');
    FORMNAME.CHIMG.focus();
    return false;
  }
  if (FORMNAME.CHIMG.value.length!=5){
    alert('zJϤҦ@'+FORMNAME.CHIMG.value.length+'X~ϤW5XƦr!!');
    FORMNAME.CHIMG.focus();
    return false;
  }
  return true;
}

<article id="post-384" class="post-384 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-allgemein tag-buendner-fussballverband tag-chur tag-dfc-ems tag-fc-ems tag-fc-thusiscazis tag-final tag-finalspiel tag-fussball tag-fussballcup tag-us-schluein-ilanz tag-valposciavo-calcio">
		<header class="entry-header">
		<div class="entry-meta"><span class="screen-reader-text">Veröffentlicht am</span> <a href="http://7451.ch/2017/05/26/buendner-fussballcup-finalspiele-2017/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-05-26T02:57:48+02:00">26. Mai 2017</time><time class="updated" datetime="2022-01-08T15:15:09+01:00">8. Januar 2022</time></a></div><!-- .entry-meta --><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://7451.ch/2017/05/26/buendner-fussballcup-finalspiele-2017/" rel="bookmark">Bündner Fussballcup Finalspiele 2017</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

			<div class="post-thumbnail">
			<a href="http://7451.ch/2017/05/26/buendner-fussballcup-finalspiele-2017/">
				<img width="960" height="641" src="http://7451.ch/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Fussballcup8b.jpeg" class="attachment-twentyseventeen-featured-image size-twentyseventeen-featured-image wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="http://7451.ch/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Fussballcup8b.jpeg 960w, http://7451.ch/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Fussballcup8b-300x200.jpeg 300w, http://7451.ch/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Fussballcup8b-768x513.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px" />			</a>
		</div><!-- .post-thumbnail -->
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Die Finalspiele des Bündner Fussballcup fanden am 25. Mai 2017 im Stadion Ringstrasse in Chur statt.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.bfv.ch/">https://www.bfv.ch/</a></p>
<p>Im Final der Damen siegte der FC Thusis/Cazis gegen den FC Ems mit 3:0.</p>
<p>Bei den Herren siegte US Schluein Ilanz gegen Valposchiavo Calcio mit 1:0.</p>
<p>Nachfolgend eine Auswahl der an diesem Tag von mir gemachten Bilder:</p>
